nd Heartbeat. Also, be sure to read Andrew Lock's piece on <a href=\"https://andrewlock.net/home-home-on-the-range-installing-kubernetes-using-rancher-2-0/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Rancher</a>, which is a bit like Portainer. I'd never heard of Rancher, it'll be interesting to do a comparison.</p>\n"}}]}}},"context":{}}